-Room-4thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>117</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>3311</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ViewOfAGuestRoom</PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/1116/64/18/81/2631759-Melia-Sol-y-Nieve-Guest-Room-5.jpg</Url><Width>480</Width><Height>316</Height><Bytes>37273</Bytes><Caption>2631759-Melia-Sol-y-Nieve-Guest-Room-5</Caption><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1116/64/18/81/2631759-Melia-Sol-y-Nieve-Guest-Room-5thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>106</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2588</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ViewOfAGuestRoom</PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/1116/64/18/81/2631759-Melia-Sol-y-Nieve-Guest-Room-6.jpg</Url><Width>480</Width><Height>293</Height><Bytes>28514</Bytes><Caption>2631759-Melia-Sol-y-Nieve-Guest-Room-6</Caption><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1116/64/18/81/2631759-Melia-Sol-y-Nieve-Guest-Room-6thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>114</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>3167</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ViewOfAGuestRoom</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>The Melia Sol y Nieve is located right in the heart of the ski resort of Sierra Nevada with excellent access to the ski slopes. The hotel was completely renovated in 2008 and is now the largest hotel in the resort and one of the most avant-garde with regards to its design and facilities. The new Melia Sol y Nieve combines the classic, unmistakable Melia style of its standard rooms with the fresh, modern design of its public areas and superior rooms and suites. A place to enjoy luxury, comfort and the superior quality details of a Melia hotel, just a few steps from the ski slopes, only 33 km from the beautiful historic city of Granada and 43 km from the airport. A privileged location for an unbeatable hotel, with personalized service, a wide range of services and facilities, the latest technology, excellent cuisine in its AQUA restaurant and the Veleta buffet and a world of sensations in the new 2,500 m2 YHI SPA, ideal for relaxation after a hard day on the slopes or at work. Come and discover the new Melia Sol y Nieve for yourself. A hotel which is passionate about service, perfect for skiing, relaxing, for business, and even for visiting Granada, one of Europe's most important cultural cities.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>The Melia Sol y Nieve is located in the entrance to the resort of Sierra Nevada, right in the centre, of the resort with easy access to the slopes. It is only 33 km from the beautiful and historic city of Granada and 43 km from its airport. It is 180 km from Malaga airport.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>4_STAR - DOUBLE - These rooms can accommodate 1 or 2 extra sofa-beds, making triple or quadruple rooms (subject to availability). Possibility of cot, on request. Services Room service from 8 am. to 11 pm. 24 hour "Serviexpress" customer service Laundry and ironing service Wake up call Up to date information on skiing conditions on TV Equipment 2 single beds Central heating Satellite TV with Canal+ and specialized channels WiFi Internet connection Telephone in room and bathroom Minibar Safe Desk Bathtub Towel radiator Hairdryer Magnifying mirror Full length mirror Arte bathroom amenities Non smoking rooms available (on request) Rooms for the disabled available (on request)

SUPERIOR - ROOM - Rooms are decorated in contemporary style with an even greater range of facilities and the latest in modern technology. All the rooms are outward-facing, bright and spacious, and measure between 26 and 33 m2. They include a hall, bathroom and lounge-bedroom and come with a sofa-bed, which means they can accommodate up to 3 people (subject to availability). Room service from 8 am. to 11 pm (extra charge) 24 hour "Serviexpress" customer service Laundry and ironing service (extra charge) Wake up call Up to date information on skiing conditions on TV Equipment: DreaMax bed Reading lamps in the bed headboard LCD satellite TV with Canal+ and theme channels CD and DVD player Minibar Heating WiFi Internet access Telephones in the bedroom and bathroom Safe free of charge Desk Luxury amenities Bathrobe and slippers Professional hairdryer Towel Radiator "Rain shower" shower room Make-up mirror Full-length mirror

